channel.title: Well
channel.description:
After having my in box spammed for the last 2 days, I'll post another picture. Lets see, 80 or so messages telling me to post more graphics is getting old to read, so I guess I can post another. [img]http://img359.imageshack.us/img359/2555/sora2lb6.png[/img]
Last night, I was asked to make a signature by somebody on another forum, I used the same techniques as above, with a different render. [img]http://img240.imageshack.us/img240/1827/iploxpikachubh7.png[/img]
--- iPlox asked me to use a different render to try and make something different, its not as good, but it works, what ya think? [img]http://img512.imageshack.us/img512/9624/iploxfi5.png[/img] ---
http://www.megaupload.com/?d=6DVT06JP http://www.megaupload.com/?d=OUTOKLQV
If you download these, I expect you to learn something. It be best if you didn't tamper with them either, or I'll have a heard of cows rape you.
